# ☕ Coffee Shop Sales Analysis

## 📌 Overview  
This project analyzes sales data from a coffee shop to optimize pricing, product offerings, and revenue growth.

## 🛠️ Tools Used  
- Power BI (for visualization)  
- SQL (for data querying)  
- Excel (for data cleaning)  

## 📊 Key Insights  
- Identified peak sales hours and best-selling products.  
- Analyzed customer purchasing trends to improve inventory management.  
- Recommended to increase the sales in weekdays as compared to weekends.  

## 📂 Files Included  
- `coffee_sales_data.xlsx` → Raw sales data  
- `coffee_shop_dashboard.pbix` → Power BI dashboard  
- `coffee_analysis.sql` → SQL queries used for analysis  

